Otv\u225\'e1ram v\u353\'61eobecn\u250\'fa rozpravu. P\u237\'edsomne sa nikto do rozpravy neprihl\u225\'e1sil. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
P\u253\'fdtam sa, kto sa hl\u225\'e1si \u250\'fastne do rozpravy. P\u225\'e1n poslanec Abrhan, p\u225\'e1n poslanec Kahanec, nikto viac. Kon\u269\'0d\u237\'edm mo\u382\'7enos\u357\'65 \u250\'fastnych prihl\u225\'e1\u353\'61ok do rozpravy. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
